                        <bop/>
                        <bos/>
                        <paratext>The Panel&apos;s deference to the transferee court in matters relating to management
                            of the litigation is pronounced.
                            <eos/>
                            <bos/>It is discussed in greater detail in Chapter 9. The Panel also defers considerably to
                            the transferee judge in determining when remand to the transferor court is appropriate.
                            <eos/>
                            <bos/>Remand is discussed in Chapter 10.
                            <eos/>
